TI  - Is there a scientific research program in memetics? - The case of bird songs
T2  - DISPUTATIO-PHILOSOPHICAL RESEARCH BULLETIN
LA  - Spanish
KW  - Meme
KW  - Cultural evolution
KW  - Cultural traditions in birds
KW  - Natural selection
