TI  - "The 'Political, Future & Accelerationism Compasses': Flat Compasses from Web Culture for a Meta-reflective Future"
T2  - V CONGRESO INTERNACIONAL DE INVESTIGACION EN ARTES VISUALES, ANIAV 2022
LA  - Spanish
