TI  - Test Case Prioritization in Unit and Integration Testing: A Shuffled-Frog-Leaping Approach
T2  - CMC-COMPUTERS MATERIALS & CONTINUA
LA  - English
KW  - Test case prioritization
KW  - unit testing
KW  - shuffled frog leaping approach
