TI  - THINKING OF A HUMAN IN THE CONTEXT OF THE MEMETIC THEORY OF RELIGION: FROM THE "IMAGE AND LIKENESS" TO THE "VEHICLE"
T2  - VESTNIK PRAVOSLAVNOGO SVYATO-TIKHONOVSKOGO GUMANITARNOGO UNIVERSITETA-SERIYA I-BOGOSLOVIE-FILOSOFIYA-RELIGIOVEDENIE
