TI  - A Self-Learning Memetic Algorithm for Human-Robot Collaboration Scheduling in Energy-Efficient Distributed Mixed Fuzzy Welding Shop
T2  - IEEE TRANSACTIONS ON AUTOMATION SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING
