TI  - Choreomanic NeuroDance and Its Aesthetics: Dance Research and Controversies Connected to Cognitive Neuroscience and Meme Theory
T2  - TABOO - TRANSGRESSION - TRANSCENDENCE IN ART AND SCIENCE (TTT 2016)
LA  - English
CP  - Interdisciplinary Conference on Taboo-Transgression-Transcendence in Art and Science
