TI  - Optimization of Component Sequencing and Feeder Assignment for a Chip Shooter Machine Using Shuffled Frog-Leaping Algorithm
T2  - IEEE TRANSACTIONS ON AUTOMATION SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING
LA  - English
